## Phase 4: Enemies + Combat

### Deliverables
Enemies spawn, patrol, chase. Stomp kills. Tail slap (F key) kills. Contact damage → knockback + invulnerability. Death → respawn.

### New Files
```
src/enemies/mod.rs            — EnemiesPlugin
src/enemies/components.rs     — Enemy, EnemyType, EnemyAI, ContactDamage
src/enemies/spawner.rs        — Spawn with Mesh3d quad + avian2d collider
src/enemies/ai.rs             — patrol, chase, return state machine
src/combat/mod.rs             — CombatPlugin
src/combat/damage.rs          — contact_damage, knockback, invulnerability, death/respawn
src/combat/stomp.rs           — Jump-on-enemy detection + kill + bounce
src/combat/tail_slap.rs       — F key hitbox attack
```

### Key Details
- Enemies: Animal Pack Redux PNGs (dog, cat, snake, parrot, rat)
- Stomp: player falling + bottom near enemy top = kill, bounce 300 velocity
- Tail slap: 28px reach in facing direction
- Health: 100 HP, 5 hearts × 20 HP. Invulnerability 1.5s.

### Agent Focus
- **Spec**: Enemy stats table, collision layer matrix, stomp geometry, tail slap hitbox
- **Implementation**: Enemy spawner, AI state machine, combat systems
- **Test**: AI state transitions, stomp from various angles, invulnerability prevents double-damage
- **Critic**: Enemies don't walk off platforms, combat feel (knockback, bounce)

