## Phase 5: Collectibles + Puzzles + All 4 Levels

### Deliverables
All 4 levels. 10 collectibles per level across 3 layers. Level gate blocks exit. Game ending at Sanctuary.

### New Files
```
src/level/subdivision.rs      — Subdivision level (houses as background art, jumpable roofs)
src/level/city.rs             — City level (industrial tiles, fire escapes)
src/level/sanctuary.rs        — Sanctuary level (nature theme)
src/collectibles/mod.rs       — CollectiblesPlugin
src/collectibles/systems.rs   — pickup on proximity, progress tracking, health food pickups
src/puzzle/mod.rs             — PuzzlePlugin
src/puzzle/systems.rs         — puzzle completion, gate, level exit, game ending
```

### Key Details
- Collectibles: Kenney food/gem tiles. Auto-pickup 24px range.
- Health food: cookie tile. Restores 20 HP.
- Level gate: 400px+ tall barrier
- Each level uses different Kenney tileset theme
- All positions validated: on ground or reachable platforms

### Agent Focus
- **Spec**: Level layouts, collectible placement ensuring reachability, gate positions
- **Implementation**: All 4 level data sets, collectible system, puzzle state machine
- **Test**: Every level loads, puzzle completion per level, gate enforcement
- **Critic**: Playtest reachability — can every collectible be reached?

