```
Phase 1 (Scaffold + Camera3d)
    ↓
Phase 2 (Physics + Controller)
    ↓
Phase 3 (Tilemap + Levels)
    ↓
Phase 4 (Enemies + Combat) ←→ Phase 5 (Collectibles + Puzzles)
                                    ↓
                              Phase 6 (HUD + Dialogue + Save/Load)
                                    ↓
                              Phase 7 (Audio + Animation)
                                    ↓
                              Phase 8 (Polish + Lighting + Effects)
```

## Verification (every phase)

- `cargo build` compiles
- `cargo test` passes
- `cargo clippy -- -D warnings` clean
- `cargo fmt --check` clean
- `cargo run` — new features visible, prior features still work
